pageProduct.name: Swisse Cranberry 90 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

SWISSE ULTIBOOST HIGH STRENGTH CRANBERRY is a premium quality formula to help support urinary tract health and provide symptomatic relief for medically diagnosed cystitis in a convenient, one-a-day dose.

BENEFITS: Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Cranberry is a premium quality formula to help support urinary tract health and provide symptomatic relief for medically diagnosed cystitis in a convenient, one-a-day dose. 

Urinary Tract Health: Supports the health and function of the urinary tract, including bladder and kidney health. 

Symptomatic Relief for Medically Diagnosed Cystitis: Provides symptomatic relief from discomfort associated with medically diagnosed cystitis such as itching, urinary odour and frequent, burning urination. 

Antioxidant Support: Cranberries are high in antioxidants, which help protect against free radical damage. Antioxidants also contribute to the maintenance of good health. 

High Potency PACran: Contains a unique powdered form of the whole cranberry fruit. 

 

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner. If pain or irritation persists for more than 48 hours - consult your doctor. The presence of blood in the urine warrants immediate medical attention.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg or artificial flavours.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:

CRANBERRY (Vaccinium macrocarpon dry fruit powder 500mg) equiv. fresh fruit 25g

Contains: Soya beans and sulfites.

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Yeast

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:

One capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25 degrees Celsius. Do not use if cap seal is broken.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Swisse is a carbon neutral company. Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
